INSERT INTO `widok_evo_site_tmplvar_contentvalues` VALUES ('1885','91','309','{\"fieldValue\":[{\"title\":\"Institute of Polish Culture, University of Warsaw\",\"url\":\"http://ikp.uw.edu.pl/dr-magda-szczesniak-2/?lang=en\"},{\"title\":\"academia.edu\",\"url\":\"http://uw.academia.edu/MagdaSzcze%C5%9Bniak\"}],\"fieldSettings\":{\"autoincrement\":1}}');
INSERT INTO `widok_evo_site_tmplvar_contentvalues` VALUES ('1886','92','309','<!-- 		@page { margin: 0.79in } 		P { margin-bottom: 0.08in; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 0; orphans: 0 } 		P.western { font-family: \"Times New Roman\", serif; font-size: 12pt; so-language: en } 		P.cjk { font-family: \"Arial Unicode MS\", sans-serif; font-size: 12pt } 		P.ctl { font-family: \"Times New Roman\", serif; font-size: 12pt; so-language: ar-SA } 		A:link { color: #0000ff } -->\n<p>Born 1985. In April 2015, she defended her Ph.D. dissertation, titled <em>Visual Constructions of Identity in the Polish Public Sphere after 1989,</em> at the Institute of Polish Culture, University of Warsaw.&nbsp;She has published articles in numerous Polish academic journals, including &bdquo;Dialog&rdquo;, &bdquo;Konteksty&rdquo;, &bdquo;Krytyka Polityczna&rdquo;, &bdquo;Kultura Wsp&oacute;łczesna&rdquo; and &bdquo;Teksty Drugie&rdquo;. In 2010, she received a Fulbright Foundation Junior Advanced Research Grant and spent a year at the University of Rochester in the framework of the Graduate Program for Visual and Cultural Studies. She was the recipient of the National Science Center &bdquo;Preludium&rdquo; grant (2013-2015) and of the Ministry of Higher Education and Science scholarship for outstanding young scholars (2017-2020). In 2017, she won the prestigious award for young scholars granted by the \"Polityka\" weekly (Nagroda Naukowa Polityki). Author of book \"Normy widzialności. Tożsamość w czasach transformacji\" [Norms of Visuality. Identity in Times of Transition], published by Fundacja Bęc Zmiana.</p>');
